    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it in pristine shape\u2014spotless interior, gleaming paint, and not a single hiccup. It\u2019s a total dream to drive. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one! Come say hi and take it for a spin; I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 42900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
