    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This is a pristine example of a well-preserved vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, chips, or door dings. It has been meticulously garage-kept and protected from the elements throughout its life. Step inside to an interior that remains in showroom state\u2014the premium leather is supple with no creasing or wear on the bolsters, the carpets are spotless, and the cabin remains entirely smoke-free. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive binder containing every service record since day one, ensuring total peace of mind for the next owner. Every button, dial, and electronic feature functions perfectly. With fresh, high-end tires and all fluids recently serviced, this vehicle is ready for a collector or a discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection.",
