      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered era. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a pristine valvetrain with recent shim adjustment and a bulletproofed dual-VANOS unit. Underneath, the chassis has been meticulously preserved, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and a complete overhaul of the trailing arm bushings. The Getrag 420G transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. Finished in concours-level paint with an interior devoid of typical UV degradation or bolster wear, this vehicle offers a visceral, high-RPM driving experience calibrated for the serious collector.",
